              "gap": 48,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "XeVyR",
                  "name": "articleBody",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "rHxpl",
                      "name": "articleText",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 20,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "svOaE",
                          "name": "para1",
                          "fill": "#272735",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "随着大语言模型规模的不断扩大，Transformer 架构面临着越来越严峻的效率挑战。自注意力机制的二次复杂度使得处理超长序列变得异常昂贵，这促使研究者们开始探索替代方案。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "dfQFv",
                          "name": "subheading1",
                          "fill": "#272735",
                          "content": "状态空间模型的崛起",
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 22,
                          "fontWeight": "500"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "ob2bC",
                          "name": "para2",
                          "fill": "#272735",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Mamba 模型的出现标志着序列建模领域的一个重要转折点。通过引入选择性状态空间机制，Mamba 实现了与 Transformer 相当的表达能力，同时将复杂度降低到线性级别。这意味着模型可以高效处理数万甚至数十万 token 的超长上下文。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "1Vik9",
                          "name": "para3",
                          "fill": "#272735",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "S4（Structured State Space for Sequences）则采用了不同的策略，通过结构化矩阵参数化来实现高效计算。实验表明，S4 在长程依赖任务上表现出色，特别是在音频和时间序列建模方面。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "xzcMk",
                          "name": "subheading2",
                          "fill": "#272735",
                          "content": "混合架构的未来",
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 22,
                          "fontWeight": "500"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "OjbSS",
                          "name": "para4",
                          "fill": "#272735",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "越来越多的证据表明，未来的最优解可能是混合架构——在需要精确注意力的层使用 Transformer，在其他层使用 SSM。这种设计既保留了 Transformer 强大的上下文理解能力，又获得了 SSM 的效率优势。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
